name: Sarah Andersen
description:
Here's a textual inversion of Sarah Andersen, a talented writer/illustrator really concerned about the evolution of AI generative tools. She's also very cute and kinda badass, so show the lady some respect !

Of course, for the long/medium shots, I use inpainting to improve the face's details. Don't hesitate to look at my prompts or message me if the result doesn't meet your expectations.

All the images generated in 512x768. You might consider to disable VAE with some models.
